Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
Located on the southern side of Wakefield Street is this terrific stand alone office building that is a landmark property in the eastern CBD precinct. With it's brilliant location, only 100 metres from the Wakefield & Hutt Street intersection, 315 Wakefield Street is an opportunity not to be missed.

Currently occupied by Kain Lawyers who are moving due to size in mid 2022, this building of 684 square metres is afforded with a functional, modern fitout that provides a high impact to clients when entering, plus an exceptional working environment for it's employees.

This space also boasts natural light provided by 2 frontages plus the sawtooth windows through the middle of the building.
Carparking for 6 cars and signage rights are also available (STC).

Lease Term: Negotiable
Options: Negotiable
Rent Reviews: Negotiable
Date Available: Mid 2022
